title: A Star Is Born - Judy Garland
description:
Album Features
Artist:	Judy Garland
Format:	CD
Release Year:	1988
Record Label:	Columbia
Genre:	Pop Vocal, Show Vocals

Track Listing
1. Overture
2. Gotta Have Me Go With You
3. The Man That Got Away
4. Born in a Trunk Medley: Swanee/I'll Get By/You Took Advantage of Me/B
5. Here's What I'm Here For
6. It's a New World
7. Someone at Last
8. Lose That Long Face

THIS WAS THE FIRST EVER CD EDITION, MADE FROM THE ORIGINAL SOUNDTRACK.  MOST OF THE TRACKS ARE STEREO, BUT A FEW ARE MONO.  ON SOME YOU CAN EVEN HEAR THE SOME OF THE CRACKS AND POPS FROM THE ORIGINAL RECORDINGS.  THE PAINSTAKING PROCESS IS CAREFULLY DESCRIBED IN THE ENCLOSED BOOKLET
